{% # Spacer block v2.0.0 %}

{% comment %}
  Changelog
  - v2.0.0 — replace the px-size settings (`breakpoint` select + `spacer_block_size` / `mobile_spacer_block_size` / `desktop_spacer_block_size` ranges) with a single `size` picker backed by the `spacing` metaobject. Same responsive contract (mobile/desktop divide rides the spacing token's `@media` branch); new interface. `background_color` unchanged. See `.context/docs/design-system-metaobjects.md` § spacing.
